  <script type="module">

            (function () {

              function getLocalVersion(consoleName) {

                return localStorage.getItem(`${consoleName.toLowerCase()}_version`) ?? "";

              }

  

              function setLocalVersion(version, consoleName) {

                console.log("setLocalVersion");

                localStorage.setItem(`${consoleName.toLowerCase()}_version`, version);

              }

  

              function setProductVersion(version, consoleName) {

               if (version !== null && consoleName) {

                  setLocalVersion(version, consoleName);

                }

                location.reload();

              }

  

              function getProductVersion(version, consoleName) {

                if (version && version.length > 0 && consoleName && consoleName.length > 0) {

                    const localVersion = getLocalVersion(consoleName);

                    if (localVersion) {

                      if (version !== localVersion) {

                        setProductVersion(version, consoleName);

                      } 

                    } else if (version !== null && consoleName.length > 0) {

                      setLocalVersion(version, consoleName);

                    }

                  }

              }

  

              function currentVersion(version, consoleName) {

                getProductVersion(version, consoleName);

              }

  

              window.currentVersion = currentVersion;

  

              const script = document.createElement("script");

              script.type = "text/javascript";

              script.src = "./version/application.js?t=" + Date.now();

              document.head.appendChild(script);

            })();

          </script>
